的，搜索，劳动的情况。”</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/haim-join-the-line-up-for-radio-1s-big-weekend-2025-3849312">HAIM已被添加到Radio 1的2025年大周末的阵容中</a>。该活动定于下个月在利物浦的塞夫顿公园举行。该小组还计划于今年夏天在巴塞罗那和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-porto-announce-stacked-2025-line-up-3810606">波尔图</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-2025-line-up-announced-tickets-3805796#:~:text=Primavera%20Sound%20have%20announced%20the,Carpenter%20all%20set%20to%20headline.">的Primavera Sound</a>露面。</p><p>同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bon-iver-drops-new-singles-if-only-i-could-wait-featuring-danielle-haim-and-walk-home-3846459">丹妮尔·海姆（Danielle Haim）与Bon Iver合作，获得了他的新单曲“如果我能等待的话”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/haims-danielle-on-new-single-everybodys-trying-to-figure-me-out-writing-it-has-gotten-me-through-some-hard-times-3851714">Haim的Post Danielle在新单曲“每个人都试图弄清楚我”上：“写作让我度过了艰难的时期”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
