//www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DavidThewlis-ValKilmer-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DavidThewlis-ValKilmer-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DavidThewlis-ValKilmer-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DavidThewlis-ValKilmer-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p>戴维·塞维利斯（David Thewlis）向他的<em>莫罗（Moreau）岛联合主演瓦尔·基尔默（Val Kilmer）岛</em>分享了他的致敬<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/batman-forever-and-top-gun-star-val-kilmer-has-died-aged-65-3851054">，后者于本周早些时候去世，享年65岁</a>。</p><p>这位<em>蝙蝠侠永远的</em>演员在与肺炎战斗后，于周二（4月1日）去世，这是他的女儿梅赛德斯（Mercedes）证实。基尔默（Kilmer）<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/val-kilmer-opens-two-year-cancer-battle-2178529">在2014年被诊断出患有喉癌</a>，但后来康复。</p><p>他的电影作品包括1996年的电影<em>《莫罗岛》（The Island of Moreau）</em> ，他在他的最后一部电影角色之一中与Marlon Brando一起看到了Kilmer和Thewlis Star。众所周知，它的生产充满了问题，尤其是基尔默（Kilmer）与白兰度（Brando）和导演约翰·弗兰肯海默（John Frankenheimer）的经常冲突。</p><p>在反思他与基尔默（Kilmer）度过的时光时，TheWlis分享了<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DH8KkX8zP7T/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram帖子</a>，以致敬他堕落的朋友。他写道：“我在澳大利亚雨林中度过了一生中最奇怪的五个月，在澳大利亚雨林中，在<em>莫罗博士命运的岛上</em>。” </p><figure id="attachment_3851717" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3851717" style="width: 1400px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3851717" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DavidThewlis-IslandofDrMoreau-Getty.jpg" alt="大卫·塞沃里斯·瓦利斯·基尔默（David Thewlis Val Kilmer）" width="1400" height="902" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DavidThewlis-IslandofDrMoreau-Getty.jpg 1400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DavidThewlis-IslandofDrMoreau-Getty-400x258.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DavidThewlis-IslandofDrMoreau-Getty-800x515.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DavidThewlis-IslandofDrMoreau-Getty-696x448.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DavidThewlis-IslandofDrMoreau-Getty-1392x897.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/DavidThewlis-IslandofDrMoreau-Getty-1068x688.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3851717" class="wp-caption-text"> Fairuza Balk和David Thewlis在“ Moreau岛”的场景中。信用：新线/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>“真是太凄凉和可怕了，几乎是很棒的。</p><p> Thewlis补充说，他回到澳大利亚时得知Kilmer的死亡：“他是我见过的最非凡的人之一。自豪地称他为朋友和同谋。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DH8KkX8zP7T/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,